commit.message:
fix(depot-map): Replace Leaflet with static OpenStreetMap iframe solution

- Removed non-loading Leaflet dynamic import
- Implemented StaticDepotMap with OSM iframe
- Direct HTML/CSS overlays for tracks and trains
- No JavaScript library dependencies
- Works immediately without loading issues
- Tracks and trains rendered as HTML elements
- Full interactivity with click handlers

This solution uses an embedded OpenStreetMap iframe with HTML overlays,
eliminating all complex JavaScript map library issues.
commit.author: Christian Schmeing
